  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to OpenJPEG</title>

    <para>
      <application>OpenJPEG</application> is an open-source implementation
      of the JPEG-2000 standard. OpenJPEG fully respects the JPEG-2000
      specifications and can compress/decompress lossless 16-bit images.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked;

